        <title>密钥分配和用户认证协议-III</title>
        <link rel="alternate" href="http://symlpigeon.github.io/2022/06/02/protocol-secure-chap4-3/"/>
        <content type="html">&lt;h1 id=&#34;非对称加密的对称密钥分发&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#非对称加密的对称密钥分发&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; 非对称加密的对称密钥分发&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;一种最朴素的密钥分发思路是这样的 (Merkle, 1979)：&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;mermaid&#34;&gt;sequenceDiagram
    loop Daily query
        Alice-&gt;&gt;Bob: Hello Bob, how are you?
        alt is sick
            Bob-&gt;&gt;Alice: Not so good :(
        else is well
            Bob-&gt;&gt;Alice: Feeling fresh like a daisy
        end
        opt Extra response
            Bob-&gt;&gt;Alice: Thanks for asking
        end
    end&lt;/pre&gt;
